{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_07_02",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 2話 壊すつもりなんかないのに",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_lesson-01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "練習お疲れ様。飲み物を買ってきたから\n少し休憩を――って、どうしたんだ、こころ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job with practice. I brought some drinks‚ so\nlet's take a break――wait‚ what's wrong‚ Kokoro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ～、{user}さんですか……\n差し入れありがとうございます……はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san…\nThanks for the refreshment… sigh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……どうしてこころしかいないんだ？\n他のみんなは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why is it only you here?\nWhere is everyone else?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4297274908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんと葵さんは走り込みです\n愛ちゃんは……分かんないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san and Aoi-san are out running.\nAi-chan… I don't know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.0429999487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かんないって……どうしたんだ？\n今日は四人でダンスレッスンのはずじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean you don't know…?\nWeren't you supposed to have a dance lesson with all four of you today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0105890593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "途中まではちゃんとレッスンしてたんですけど\n休憩中に愛ちゃんと喧嘩しちゃって……あはは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were practicing together until a break‚ but\nAi-chan and I had a fight during the break… haha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "喧嘩って……もしかして、例の衣装の件か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A fight… is it about the outfit issue?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2052830855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "はい。莉央さんと葵さんは\n頭を冷やして二人で話し合え、って出て行っちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Rio-san and Aoi-san\ntold us to cool our heads and talk it out‚ so they left.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なら、愛はどこにいるんだ？　話し合いは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ where's Ai? What happened to the discussion…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6114734489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "それが……愛ちゃんは今回の件に限っては\n絶対に譲らないって。本気の喧嘩になっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… Ai-chan said she absolutely wouldn't budge on this.\nIt turned into a serious fight‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8014437198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんも、出て行っちゃいました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and Ai-chan left too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1423122246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "愛がそんなに頑なになるなんてめずらしいな\nこころがどんなに悪ふざけをしても許してくれるのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's rare for Ai to be so stubborn.\nShe usually forgives you no matter how much you fool around.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1982750419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ。愛ちゃんは私の親友で、とっても優しくて\nこころが何をしても怒らなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Ai-chan is my best friend and so kind‚\nshe never gets angry no matter what I do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　まるでこころがいつも愛ちゃんに\n迷惑を掛けてるみたいな言い方ですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wait! That makes it sound like\nI always trouble Ai-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（自覚がなかったのか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She didn't realize that…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.681792577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに愛ちゃんの頭が固いなんて\n思いもしませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never imagined\nAi-chan could be so stubborn.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてこころの気持ちを\n分かってくれないんでしょう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why doesn't she understand\nhow I feel…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.8310615431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "まずは少し落ち着こう\nそれから詳しく話を聞かせてくれないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's calm down first.\nThen can you tell me the details?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1844427749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "…………はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4333343506,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3064.3975810999964,
          "startTime": 116.4977319317
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 116.2477319317
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 116.2477319317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sigh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2977319317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "プリン、好きだったよな？　全然食べてないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You liked pudding‚ right? You haven't touched it at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2644212839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "食欲がわきません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't have an appetite.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6393865861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.5658769008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんとはこれまで一杯喧嘩しましたけど\nこんなにギスギスした雰囲気になったのは初めてです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai-chan and I have had lots of fights before‚ but\nthis is the first time it's felt so tense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "愛は新しい衣装を作るのに反対らしいけど……\nどうして反対してるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai seems to be against making new outfits…\nWhy is she opposed to it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.9077111726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.3605407433
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "あの曲……『GIRI-GIRI\nborderless world』は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That song… \"GIRI-GIRI\nborderless world\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんにとっても、特別思い入れのある曲なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "is very special to Ai-chan too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5022292174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 149.606882687
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "デビュー前、くじけそうになった時\n一緒にステージで観たあの曲に救ってもらったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before our debut‚ when she felt like giving up‚\nthat song we watched together on stage saved her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.2999908447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.3580480453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 158.4235088623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
